### Co-located in `PendingSyncQueue`
Reconciliation is a **`private static func`** on `PendingSyncQueue`, so it stays an implementation detail of the queue with no empty `enum` wrapper. It works in terms of app-layer **`Delta`** (from `OnlineStorage.swift`) end-to-end, so there’s no extra DTO.

